{"tid":1909062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［功組］蕭生大絕：將逼使各食肆表態功能組別，否則將其標籤及宣傳為藍店！","createTime":"2020-03-03T16:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T17:52:37.000Z","uid":219007,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ee70759ac6ee9eda2e0317098c53732fa813815c","tid":1909062,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:51:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8dyHr2lneOY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8dyHr2lneOY&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=76bdb42a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8dyHr2lneOY</a><br />\n<br />\n「功能組別緊急呼籲！轉達長毛訊息，馬上備戰，寸土必爭！」〈蕭若元：理論蕭析〉2020-03-02<br />\n<br />\n蕭生聯同民主動力使出大絕，一定要推銷蕭生講嗰幾個界別，一個係飲食界。 係飲食界係要啲鋪頭表態，即係中間嗰啲表態，你願唔願意投反對投張宇人嗰啲先？如果你唔贊成我哋就會覺得你係藍店，並向外加以宣傳你呢間藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲鋪頭今次一定淆晒底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b18bcab159b186c1dc54980608c0b7ad28bd12b","tid":1909062,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8169855dbeb8948cd486639b014aecc867cbd17","tid":1909062,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:53:57.000Z","msg":"支持燒山！"},{"pid":"cedb7978703b3bc7ebc89061a694cfa090243ea0","tid":1909062,"uid":150483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"姐係功能組別要佢地交表申謝先投到？"},{"pid":"965c84c9288deefbe6a5450a903229a1fe997b03","tid":1909062,"uid":171506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:55:37.000Z","msg":"唔表態，燒山就祝